OL,3,CHow to spot a shooting star in
OL,4,Ctonight's Quadrantid meteor shower
OL,6,FThe shower's peak is at 3pm on Friday,
OL,7,Fbefore it is fully dark, but meteors
OL,8,Fshould still be visible later into
OL,9,FFriday evening.
OL,11,FHow can I see them?
OL,13,FUnlike many astronomical events,
OL,14,Fmeteor showers are easy to watch and
OL,15,Fdo not require any special equipment
OL,16,Fto be enjoyed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
